{"tid":915043,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"進攻單調幾乎輸埋 曼聯0:0吞「晶」失敗","createTime":"2018-11-24T17:11:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-24T17:26:53.000Z","uid":151982,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3746d6da577191f6d2220866d4f2d16e4e51de4c","tid":915043,"uid":151982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T17:11:28.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=lC4QaT1FYrLfR%2FOZUP8DPZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=c7f785fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】曼聯在周末英超再次暴露攻力不足的問題，在主場與攻勢更到肉的水晶宮悶和0:0，賽後已落後曼城14分之多。<br />\n<br />\n與國際賽前不敵曼城比較，曼聯共作出4個正選調動，包括保羅普巴及盧卡古，至於水晶宮有韋費特沙夏復出倒戈。曼聯早段就有連格接應盧卡古回傳後施射省中人不入，然而虛火過後，較似提早把皮球送進網窩的一隊，是水晶宮。<br />\n<br />\n17分鐘，曼聯予沙夏太多空位，惟這名倒戈兵射高。3分鐘後，又是沙夏，然而他在禁區頂起腳皮球貼柱出界。25分鐘，水晶宮又在一次快攻中由沙夏撥交，雲安荷特卻射斜。完半場前，高耶迪入波卻被判越位在先。<br />\n<br />\n易邊後13分鐘，輪到盧卡古入波卻被判越位在先，入球作廢。水晶宮依然是埋門更入肉的一隊，唐辛在一次快速推進中施射斜出。曼聯在中段起先後換入拉舒福特、費蘭尼及阿歷斯山齊士，但攻勢單調。<br />\n<br />\n84分鐘，盧卡古頭球攻門被對方門將軒尼斯奮勇撲出底線，而其後福仔又埋門失機，最終主場又失分。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/25/011023_42af5dc73f5514c29e409d776e46c46c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F25%2F011023_42af5dc73f5514c29e409d776e46c46c.jpg&h=9ed6fd89&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e84bd5845ffa7a3f15cc844722cc83b31d2c3a66","tid":915043,"uid":34858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T17:15:20.000Z","msg":"水晶宮太黑仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 入唔到波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f224f2108986a1956236d968dacd2c77148dc63d","tid":915043,"uid":89595,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T17:16:18.000Z","msg":"點睇都係水晶宮失分多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13fdf4c8f006d2ececef746579c589824f704e53","tid":915043,"uid":124292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T17:17:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.24.co.za/files/Cms/General/d/8167/6f19731580294ba2bad889f8dfa53048.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.24.co.za%2Ffiles%2FCms%2FGeneral%2Fd%2F8167%2F6f19731580294ba2bad889f8dfa53048.jpg&h=bc642f98&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6e041bc52fd4b00e59e9d37ba8daf92935a84a6a","tid":915043,"uid":74278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T17:26:53.000Z","msg":"呑晶會唔會核突左啲"}]}